2 accounting for transformer age and condition using ANSI/IEEE Standard C57.110 and IEEE
3 Standard C57.91.
4 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the state should identify hardware solutions to
5 block GIC from entering the grid, ascertain the total costs to implement this GIC protection
6 and explore funding, including federal grants, to cover the associated costs of this GIC
7 protection.
8 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to
9 Louisiana Public Service Commission, the governor, the Louisiana Congressional
10 Delegation, the Secretary of Energy, and the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission.
